Currently, as soon as you see a card in editor/browser, it's "edited" value is changed. This means that you can't really know when a note was edited for the last time. This add-on correct this, and wait until a change is really made to change the "edited" value.



To report bug, and for more informations, please go to https://github.com/Arthur-Milchior/anki-dont-change-edited-uselessly

